  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/1735",
  "title": "[Docs] Feedback",
  "body": "The documentation is gorgeous!\r\n\r\nHere are a few suggestions that would improve readability IMHO:\r\n\r\n1. Decrease padding between header and the start of the content:\r\n![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/5570853/21102996/d0c5b9b8-c080-11e6-9d71-ce567bdb053b.png)\r\n\r\n2. Remove or ligthen the background pattern of the code examples. It looks very nice, but very disturbing when you actually try to read the code:\r\n![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/5570853/21103016/ef456a64-c080-11e6-8ff6-7a20f4c8b884.png)\r\n\r\n3. Increase the `<p>` line height a bit to make it inline code snippets \"breathe\":\r\n![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/5570853/21103080/2bd08612-c081-11e6-9266-989d4ffb78cf.png)\r\n\r\n4. Add some padding to the bottom of the sidebar:\r\n![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/5570853/21103095/40036f64-c081-11e6-8437-41c555dac6ad.png)\r\n\r\nWDYT?",
